---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — ByteBrew Engine" description="ByteBrew Engine Privacy Policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Last modified: March 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          ByteBrew ("we", "us", "our") operates bytebrew.ai. This
          policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>Account data: email address, hashed password</li>
          <li>Payment data: processed by Stripe (we don't store card numbers)</li>
          <li>Usage metadata: login timestamps, feature usage counts</li>
          <li>Technical data: IP address, browser type (for security)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
          <li>Process payments and manage subscriptions</li>
          <li>Send transactional emails (password reset, billing)</li>
          <li>Improve our products and services</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We share data only with:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>Stripe (payment processing)</li>
          <li>Resend (transactional email delivery)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-text-primary">
          We never sell your data to third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>Active accounts: data stored while account exists</li>
          <li>Deleted accounts: personal data purged within 30 days</li>
          <li>Billing records: retained as required by law</li>
          <li>Anonymized usage data may be retained indefinitely</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
          <li>Export your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of non-essential communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@bytebrew.ai" class="text-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent-hover">info@bytebrew.ai</a> to exercise these rights.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">7. Cookies & Local Storage</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>We use localStorage for authentication tokens</li>
          <li>No third-party tracking cookies</li>
          <li>No advertising cookies</li>
          <li>Optional: analytics via Plausible (privacy-friendly, no cookies)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">8. Security</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-text-tertiary">
          <li>All data transmitted over HTTPS/TLS</li>
          <li>Passwords hashed with bcrypt</li>
          <li>API tokens hashed with SHA-256</li>
          <li>Regular security reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
          an updated "Last modified" date. Continued use after changes constitutes
          acceptance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          For privacy-related questions: <a href="mailto:info@bytebrew.ai" class="text-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent-hover">info@bytebrew.ai</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          For general support: <a href="mailto:support@bytebrew.ai" class="text-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent-hover">support@bytebrew.ai</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
